Super delicious cake recipe ....

1.  Place a bowl of eggs on a pot of hot water, add sugar, honey, and vanilla extract, stir and mix until the temperature reaches 40 degrees.  2 .  Whip until a rich ivory-colored foam is obtained with a hand mixer, then sift through the flour and mix.  3.  Put a little bit of the dough in a bowl of melted unsalted butter and milk (temperature 50 to 60 degrees), mix, put in the main dough, mix, and transfer about a third of the dough to another bowl.  |  4 .  Mix the mixed dough with strawberry powder + warm milk and pink and white food coloring. Mix the other dough with cocoa powder + warm milk.  5.  Pour two pieces of dough into the mold, flatten it, and bake and cool for 30 minutes in an oven preheated to 170 degrees.
 6.  Cut the top, bottom, and edges of the cooled sheet and prepare it by cutting into a long rectangular shape.  7.  Add strawberry jam to cream cheese, mix fresh cream and mix to make cream.  8 .  Apply the cream between the chocolate and strawberry sheets alternately, and stack 2 times.  9.  Cut off both ends, apply the cream evenly over the ground, and set for 30 minutes in the freezer.  10.  Pour ganache of about 28 to 30 degrees onto the cake and coat it.
